Singer Avril has showered music director Jibril Blessing with so much love now that he is celebrating his birthday. The singer shared three Instagram messages dotted with heart emojis, wishing her ‘love’ prosperity in the new year. She wrote, "Happy Birthday. I thank God for you. Happy Birthday. Thanking God for you." The two have been rumoured to be dating for the longest time now. Blessing is also said to have fathered Avril’s baby, according to numerous media outlets, but has always kept it private. Radio presenter Mwende Macharia also has a child with J Blessing. She also celebrated his birthday with a message, saying, "Happy birthday to you, Baba Champ."